Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千沙都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容子！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手塚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類並不是只有憎恨而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你們 快理解啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 CDC
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分離這個區塊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分離N區塊 急速排除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不讓你從這裡逃走！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙想要去哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是有…弓子在啊…
